which directed amendment of section “2124(h)(3)” of this title by substituting “designated under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4121/b"},"text":"section 4121(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":"” for “designated under section 1105 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2010 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84"},"text":"Public Law 111–84","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2358"},"text":"10 U.S.C. 2358","children":[],"tail":" note)”, was executed by making the substitution in subsec. (h)(3) of this section to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—Subsec. (f)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92","children":[],"tail":" substituted “transaction” for “transition”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—Subsecs. (f) to (h). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (f) and redesignated former subsecs. (f) and (g) as (g) and (h), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idaa5b58fe-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idaa5b58ff-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2021 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s215"},"text":"section 215 of Pub. L. 117–81","children":[],"tail":" effective immediately after the effective date of the amendments made by title XVIII of "},{"tag":"ref","att